1
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,880
Why is it called Ten City?

2
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,280
Is he Prince Shi?

3
00:01:06,079 --> 00:01:06,920
Well, this city

4
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:07,920
was originally called Thousand City.

5
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:09,359
After the new Prince Shi took office,

6
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:10,200
it was renamed Ten City.

7
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:13,680
But this new Prince Shi is a bit odd.

8
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:15,799
His only wish since childhood

9
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:17,640
has been to renovate the manor,

10
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:18,879
expand its old structure,

11
00:01:19,359 --> 00:01:22,079
inscribe poems of sages upon it,

12
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:24,359
and have writings composed to commemorate it.

13
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,560
But due to tight finances,

14
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,480
it's always been rejected.

15
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,359
Ah!

16
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,599
So poor?

17
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,079
Then I'd better not marry him.

18
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,280
As if anyone would want to marry you.

19
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,480
Hey!

20
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,959
What do you mean by that?

21
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,760
You're saying nobody wants me, huh?

22
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,959
And now you're covering my ears?

23
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,560
Spit it out!

24
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:52,280
Huh?

25
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,280
What's this?

26
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:53,959
Ouch!

27
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,519
Stop butting in.

28
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,879
This arena will host, in five days,

29
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,920
a mixed-gender Seven Wounds Fist tournament.

30
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:03,200
Participants must be one man and one woman.

31
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:07,000
The winning team will receive a grand prize.

32
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,159
You're not thinking of entering, are you?

33
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,560
A contest of this level,

34
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,599
this Princess couldn't care less about.

35
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:15,120
Let's go.

36
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:18,719
Haha.

37
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:21,479
You martial-world folks really are strange.

38
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:24,560
What's so appealing about this prize?

39
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,080
Huh?

40
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,360
Would anyone really enter for a prize like this?

41
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,360
Hey.

42
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,120
Hey!

43
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:36,520
Hey!

44
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,280
Hmm?

45
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,680
Don't even think about it.

46
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,360
The Seven Wounds Fist is so easy.

47
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,400
I can teach you.

48
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,319
Come on, help me out.

49
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,199
I can't learn it.

50
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,120
You haven't even tried and you know you can't?

51
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:06,400
What prize do you even want?

52
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,319
Don't you already have the manuals?

53
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,680
For a portrait, just ask the Crown Prince.

54
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:11,520
If you want a slingshot, I'll buy you one.

55
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,319
No.

56
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:13,879
I'm entering, no matter what.

57
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,479
Didn't think Prince Shi was so handsome.

58
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,560
I don't need you anymore.

59
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:38,919
Greetings, Prince Shi.

60
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:40,680
We two are envoys sent from the palace.

61
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,520
Oh.

62
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:49,080
Greetings, envoys.

63
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,120
Here's the situation.

64
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,520
The late Emperor has passed away,

65
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,599
and the Crown Prince sent us to find a successor.

66
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,919
Passing through Ten City, I saw the people thriving.

67
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:57,479
Would Prince Shi return with us to inherit the throne?

68
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:58,719
Prince Shi! Prince Shi!

69
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,520
Pardon the spectacle.

70
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,360
Please, wait a moment.

71
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,000
If there are no objections,

72
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,800
then please return to the capital with us, Prince Shi.

73
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,319
B-b-but...

74
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,600
I haven't...

75
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,079
I haven't...

76
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,120
left this manor in over a decade.

77
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,079
I'm afraid

78
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,720
I can't step outside.

79
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,800
I just can't.

80
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:47,000
Ugh.

81
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,879
Then you cannot inherit the throne.

82
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,519
Wishing you a speedy recovery, Prince Shi.

83
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,360
We'll take our leave.

84
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,079
Hey, hey!

85
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,079
Wait a moment.

86
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:56,639
I...

87
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:58,199
I'm willing to inherit the throne.

88
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,079
But on one condition.

89
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,439
You have to help me

90
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,519
get outside.

91
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,240
Oh.

92
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,360
Of course he can't do it.

93
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,759
Do you know the Seven Wounds Fist?

94
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:09,560
Yes.

95
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,199
Then if you become emperor,

96
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:14,480
will you marry me, make me your empress,

97
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,360
help restore my kingdom, and not share my bed?

98
00:05:17,079 --> 00:05:18,480
No sharing a bed.

99
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:22,879
Wouldn't that be wonderful?

100
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,319
Deal.

101
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:34,279
What's wrong with this path?

102
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,279
Look at all these lines.

103
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,519
Crisscrossing everywhere.

104
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,120
How am I supposed to step over them?

105
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,920
Because of this?

106
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,199
What do you mean "because of this"?

107
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,079
Do you know how, to a Virgo,

108
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:50,639
this, this, this...

109
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:53,680
how terrifying this whole thing is?

110
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,600
You won't even tell us what you're looking for.

111
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,759
He just can't step on the lines, right?

112
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:20,120
So let's just keep him from seeing them.

113
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,720
Carry him out.

114
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,079
Come on.

115
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:30,920
I'll help you up.

116
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:31,600
No, no, no.

117
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,160
I'll do it myself.

118
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:35,920
Fine.

119
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,240
See?

120
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,240
It's really simple.

121
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,000
I'm afraid

122
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,800
I stepped on a line.

123
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,519
Come on.

124
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,800
Don't, don't, don't!

125
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,680
Don't move!

126
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:12,680
You...

127
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,160
I'm afraid...

128
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,720
I'm afraid you stepped on a line too.

129
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,480
Ugh.

130
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:21,519
So Royal Brother has this kind of OCD.

131
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,480
That can't be cured anytime soon.

132
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:28,879
Looks like I don't need to worry this time.

133
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,920
Heh, heh, heh, heh.

134
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,360
Come on.

135
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:35,879
Prince Shi.

136
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:38,000
I really can't try anymore.

137
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,079
Just let me be.

138
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,000
Open your eyes and look.

139
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,360
Try taking a few steps.

140
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,399
It really seems fine now.

141
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,360
Oh my goodness!

142
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,560
I'm so happy!

143
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,519
My joy is truly beyond words.

144
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:09,480
Thank you both, thank you both!

145
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,160
I'm really so happy!

146
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,079
I told you,

147
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,920
just leave it to me.

148
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,720
Why don't I believe it's that simple?

149
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:21,079
Don't worry.

150
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,519
As long as we get him out

151
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,199
before Liu Heng shows up,

152
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,360
there'll be no problem.

153
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,279
Hey,

154
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,639
but that whatever-sign thing,

155
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,720
what is it exactly?

156
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,360
Before I came to Ten City,

157
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,720
I specially studied Western astrology.

158
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,759
According to the Western zodiac,

159
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,480
there are 12 signs in total.

160
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:43,200
The position of the stars at your birth corresponds to a sign.

161
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,559
And this sign

162
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:47,480
shapes your personality, traits, charm, and career.

163
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,000
Come on, get to the point!

164
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,559
The point is,

165
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,840
Prince Shi

166
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,799
happens to be

167
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,879
the most criticized one,

168
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,519
a

169
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,759
Vir

170
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,919
go.

171
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:01,440
This sign

172
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:05,399
is obsessed with perfection, nitpicky, and tense.

173
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:07,159
Not only do they have severe germaphobia,

174
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:08,759
but also OCD.

175
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:11,360
He drives himself crazy, and everyone

176
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:13,919
around him too.

177
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:16,759
A report, Your Highness.

178
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:20,320
Prince Shi,

179
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:23,320
ten days ago, four villages suffered a locust plague.

180
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:25,080
There will surely be many refugees.

181
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:28,000
We should hurry to set up seven porridge stalls in the next two days,

182
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:30,200
two each at the east, west, and north gates,

183
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,159
and one at the south gate.

184
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,879
Why only one at the south gate?

185
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,519
Uh...

186
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,080
I'm asking you,

187
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,120
why only one at the south gate?

188
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,279
There are four gates in total.

189
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:45,559
Why can't they all be neat and symmetrical?

190
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:48,200
Are you deliberately trying to infuriate me?!

191
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,200
No, no, no!

192
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,279
Prince Shi, please don't be angry!

193
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,360
I'll fix it right away,

194
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,399
right away!

195
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,480
Whoa!

196
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:55,919
What's that tuft of hair on your face?

197
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,360
There's a huge clump of mud on your foot.

198
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:09,480
Are you hinting to me

199
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,000
that your salary isn't enough?

200
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,720
Come on, Prince Shi.

201
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:14,799
They all look perfectly fine to me.

202
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:17,600
You're just nitpicking.

203
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,960
You've got the nerve to step forward?

204
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:26,559
Why are you only carrying one sword?

205
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,200
It looks good.

206
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:28,960
Huh?

207
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,799
Can't you carry two swords, symmetrically crossed?

208
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,799
That looks good!

209
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:35,159
Don't you have any sense of aesthetics?

210
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,320
Heh.

211
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:38,360
Why don't you mention you're carrying just one sword yourself?

212
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,519
Hey, forget it, forget it.

213
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,080
Hold your tongue. Calm down.

214
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:42,200
And you!

215
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,159
Who allowed you to bring a chicken into the hall?

216
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,080
Every single one of you!

217
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,399
A chicken in the great hall!

218
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:52,120
Are you all blind?

219
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,080
Please calm down, Prince Shi.

220
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,879
Please calm down, Prince Shi.

221
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,399
I'm furious!

222
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,720
Guards!

223
00:10:58,679 --> 00:11:00,000
Drag them all out!

224
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,000
Hey!

225
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:03,559
Spare us!

226
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,559
Mercy, Prince Shi!

227
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:06,799
You're going way too far!

228
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,919
Help me.

229
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,600
My condition is getting worse again.

230
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,279
I can't control myself.

231
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:17,399
Prince Shi.

232
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:19,120
You should really call a physician.

233
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,720
We really can't help you.

234
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:24,679
I've already seen every physician in town.

235
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,320
None of them work.

236
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,559
I can help.

237
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,919
Don't make it weird like last time.

238
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:34,480
Do you remember what you promised me?

239
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,519
I promised to marry you,

240
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,960
make you my empress,

241
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,600
help restore your kingdom,

242
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,960
and not share a bed with you.

243
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,120
And what else?

244
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:47,240
And join you in the Seven Wounds Fist contest in five days,

245
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:48,960
to take first place.

246
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,879
So I will definitely cure you.

247
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,320
Starting today,

248
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:54,480
I'll take over your daily routine.

249
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:55,720
Really?

250
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:59,679
Since I got you out of this manor,

251
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:01,519
I can definitely cure you.

252
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,200
Let's go.

253
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,279
Get ready.

254
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,240
Let's go.

255
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,039
Get ready.

256
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:23,639
Younger Brother.

257
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,240
Royal Brother.

258
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,519
Even with my fan covering my face like this,

259
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,159
you still recognized me?

260
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,159
You.

261
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,279
After all these years,

262
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,120
you still love sneaking in the back way.

263
00:12:36,279 --> 00:12:37,120
Me?

264
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,320
Look at your bangs.

265
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:42,200
Why are they parted to the side?

266
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,279
That looks awful.

267
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,759
Try a middle part.

268
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,759
Hey.

269
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:51,200
Royal Brother,

270
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,279
it's been over ten years,

271
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:57,120
and your OCD is still bone-deep.

272
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:58,480
Well,

273
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,320
what can I say? I'm a Virgo.

274
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,000
But,

275
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:03,120
recently, thanks to the two envoys

276
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,519
and a good friend,

277
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:07,879
sigh.

278
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,679
Tomorrow,

279
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:11,279
I'll head to the capital to inherit the throne.

280
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,919
When that time comes,

281
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:16,039
Younger Brother, you must come visit me.

282
00:13:16,039 --> 00:13:16,919
Mm.

283
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:19,559
Royal Brother,

284
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:22,000
I'm afraid by then,

285
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,559
I won't be able to see you.

286
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:25,240
You...

287
00:13:25,879 --> 00:13:26,480
Guards!

288
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:28,159
Bring the scissors.

289
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,000
Royal Brother,

290
00:13:34,159 --> 00:13:36,600
how could you dirty your hands with such a task?

291
00:13:36,919 --> 00:13:37,759
How about this:

292
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:38,720
you rest first,

293
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:39,759
and I'll do it myself.

294
00:13:40,279 --> 00:13:41,080
Goodbye.

295
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:47,960
Ouyang Yan, stop causing us trouble!

296
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,960
He's so sick, how could you possibly cure him?

297
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,759
Prince Shi is so gravely ill right now,

298
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:54,080
how can you bear to ignore it?

299
00:13:55,399 --> 00:13:56,320
What are you looking at?

300
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:58,720
This.

301
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,120
I got it from Prince Shi's personal maid.

302
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:04,679
Prince Shi's 580 Rules of Daily Living.

303
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:07,080
Prince Shi really is seriously ill.

304
00:14:07,559 --> 00:14:08,639
Take a look.

305
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,679
"Must rise at a quarter past the Hour of the Dragon,

306
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:12,360
within a fifteen-minute limit,

307
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,399
to wash and change clothes."

308
00:14:13,919 --> 00:14:16,759
"Breakfast daily at three quarters past the Hour of the Snake.

309
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:19,679
Must eat one dish from the left, one from the right,

310
00:14:19,679 --> 00:14:21,519
maintaining the balance of two bowls of porridge."

311
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,159
That's insane!

312
00:14:25,279 --> 00:14:26,759
There's still time to switch princes!

313
00:14:26,799 --> 00:14:27,720
No.

314
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:29,759
Since we've already got this manual,

315
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:32,480
we'll start by breaking these rules.

316
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,279
We'll definitely cure Prince Shi.

317
00:14:34,279 --> 00:14:34,720
Hmph.

318
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:35,559
Hey,

319
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,879
just spare Prince Shi already.

320
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,120
Huh?

321
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:48,919
Wake up!

322
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,279
What time is it?

323
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:54,759
I don't know.

324
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:57,720
You have to tell me what time it is!

325
00:14:57,919 --> 00:14:59,120
I really don't know.

326
00:14:59,279 --> 00:15:01,960
Every timekeeping device in your residence,

327
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,600
I knocked them all

328
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,600
down.

329
00:15:04,879 --> 00:15:05,600
Hey!

330
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,000
What about my night watchman?

331
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,200
I knocked him out too!

332
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,120
How could you do this?

333
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,559
Without knowing the time, I'll fall apart!

334
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,360
I won't know what to do next!

335
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,120
Let me tell you.

336
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:19,159
You'll spend all day practicing the Seven Wounds Fist with me.

337
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,480
The contest is starting soon.

338
00:15:20,519 --> 00:15:22,000
You haven't trained with me yet.

339
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,120
No, no way!

340
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,480
That's not in my schedule.

341
00:15:26,759 --> 00:15:27,799
I must,

342
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,320
I must start keeping time now!

343
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:30,919
Prince Shi.

344
00:15:31,879 --> 00:15:33,759
This is the last hourglass.

345
00:15:34,399 --> 00:15:35,200
Good.

346
00:15:35,799 --> 00:15:36,799
Very good.

347
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,720
Start counting from now.

348
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,919
I must dine within one hour.

349
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:41,480
Meet with my officials an hour after.

350
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,639
All of today's plans

351
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,519
will go by this hourglass.

352
00:15:44,759 --> 00:15:45,360
Ah!

353
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:49,480
Hahahahahaha!

354
00:15:52,519 --> 00:15:53,120
Prince Shi.

355
00:15:53,279 --> 00:15:53,759
Hmm?

356
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:57,480
The best cure for OCD is fighting fire with fire.

357
00:15:58,320 --> 00:16:01,279
Start with every detail of a Virgo's life,

358
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:04,559
completely shatter all his obsessions,

359
00:16:04,879 --> 00:16:07,120
until the patient totally breaks down,

360
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:10,679
ultimately achieving a fresh start through destruction.

361
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:13,919
That's the treatment for Prince Shi.

362
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:14,919
Ah!

363
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:16,480
Breakdown therapy!

364
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:27,639
I...

365
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:28,399
You...

366
00:16:29,159 --> 00:16:29,960
He...

367
00:16:46,919 --> 00:16:47,720
You!

368
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:04,400
Ah!

369
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,400
A ghost!

370
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,160
Ghost? What ghost?

371
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:06,519
I...

372
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,920
You've been sneaking around for days.

373
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:10,720
What are you looking for?

374
00:17:11,279 --> 00:17:12,119
None of your business.

375
00:17:17,519 --> 00:17:20,359
Imperial Father gave him plenty of treasures back then.

376
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:23,920
I remember every gift Imperial Father gave each prince and princess.

377
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,200
Once I become emperor,

378
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,920
I'll take every single one back.

379
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:28,480
Hmph.

380
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,119
You hold grudges like that?

381
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:30,359
A Scorpio, I bet.

382
00:17:30,599 --> 00:17:31,599
None of your business.

383
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,119
Hey, let me have a look.

384
00:17:35,279 --> 00:17:36,119
Here.

385
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,119
Finally found it!

386
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,279
This was a gift from Imperial Father to me!

387
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:54,519
Hmph.

388
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:03,680
Come on.

389
00:18:04,279 --> 00:18:06,119
Left hand, hold my right hand.

390
00:18:14,359 --> 00:18:14,680
Hurry up!

391
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,599
Are you kidding me?

392
00:18:33,559 --> 00:18:34,119
Hey...

393
00:18:37,279 --> 00:18:38,119
My patience

394
00:18:38,759 --> 00:18:41,519
has completely run out!

395
00:18:42,599 --> 00:18:43,400
Prince Shi.

396
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:45,279
Prince Shi!

397
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:49,119
Prince Shi!

398
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,680
What are you doing under the bed?

399
00:18:57,079 --> 00:18:58,799
Today's bedtime has passed.

400
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:02,200
I'll wait till tomorrow's bedtime to sleep.

401
00:19:03,359 --> 00:19:05,519
But that's a whole night away!

402
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,440
Then what

403
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,720
are you doing?

404
00:19:07,799 --> 00:19:08,720
Waiting for daybreak.

405
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,079
Disinfecting

406
00:19:12,079 --> 00:19:14,319
won't drown my sorrows.

407
00:19:16,799 --> 00:19:17,599
Come on.

408
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:36,519
Prince Shi.

409
00:19:37,519 --> 00:19:38,960
Have you always been like this?

410
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,799
It's because I'm a Virgo.

411
00:19:44,519 --> 00:19:46,119
I know I'm strange.

412
00:19:46,359 --> 00:19:47,400
Ever since I was little,

413
00:19:47,519 --> 00:19:49,279
the other princes never wanted to play with me.

414
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:50,480
Because

415
00:19:50,839 --> 00:19:52,359
I thought they were dirty.

416
00:19:52,799 --> 00:19:54,519
I didn't dare play cuju or wrestle with them.

417
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:58,759
So I'm grateful to you and Qi Zhi.

418
00:19:59,599 --> 00:20:00,720
Especially you.

419
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:05,480
I've been eccentric since childhood,

420
00:20:06,079 --> 00:20:07,480
and never really had any friends,

421
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:12,319
let alone shared drinks with a close friend.

422
00:20:12,319 --> 00:20:13,200
Whether the treatment

423
00:20:13,519 --> 00:20:15,519
works in the end or not,

424
00:20:16,359 --> 00:20:17,680
I'm already content.

425
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,720
Thank you.

426
00:20:22,279 --> 00:20:23,079
Sigh.

427
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:29,519
Prince Shi.

428
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:31,240
Don't worry.

429
00:20:31,599 --> 00:20:33,279
I'll definitely cure you.

430
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:36,160
Mm.

431
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,200
Prince Shi.

432
00:20:40,519 --> 00:20:42,720
To deal with Prince Shi,

433
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:44,759
others prescribe the right medicine.

434
00:20:45,279 --> 00:20:46,119
But we

435
00:20:46,119 --> 00:20:48,119
can prescribe the right poison.

436
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:50,279
Poison him?

437
00:20:55,279 --> 00:20:56,119
Hey!

438
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:57,680
Hey!

439
00:20:57,799 --> 00:20:58,759
No, no, no, no!

440
00:20:58,759 --> 00:21:00,680
I'm not telling you to go buy arsenic!

441
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:03,160
Young Prince,

442
00:21:04,359 --> 00:21:06,200
to deal with Prince Shi,

443
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:08,279
just a few words will do.

444
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,200
Oh.

445
00:21:16,839 --> 00:21:17,880
Prince Shi.

446
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:19,480
Prince Shi!

447
00:21:39,559 --> 00:21:40,880
Thank you, thank you.

448
00:21:57,319 --> 00:21:58,599
Fish for sale! Fish for sale!

449
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:01,279
Come take a look!

450
00:22:01,279 --> 00:22:02,119
Fresh fish!

451
00:22:03,119 --> 00:22:03,680
Sir!

452
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:04,440
Come and look!

453
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:09,319
Fish for sale!

454
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:16,559
What are you doing?

455
00:22:16,559 --> 00:22:18,079
How can I see you if you're behind me?

456
00:22:21,359 --> 00:22:22,599
I won't let you get your way.

457
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:23,519
Hmph.

458
00:22:27,519 --> 00:22:30,799
Lost his mind.

459
00:22:31,279 --> 00:22:31,720
Princess.

460
00:22:32,279 --> 00:22:33,519
I told you,

461
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,880
I would come.

462
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,160
Let's go up.

463
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:40,559
It's your turn.

464
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:49,559
What are you doing here?

465
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,160
I came to watch

466
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,720
Prince Shi fight.

467
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:05,319
Royal Brother.

468
00:23:05,759 --> 00:23:07,279
Don't rush into the match yet.

469
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:09,720
Look, what's this?

470
00:23:26,279 --> 00:23:27,480
An imperial decree!

471
00:23:35,319 --> 00:23:36,400
By the Mandate of Heaven,

472
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,759
the Emperor proclaims:

473
00:23:38,119 --> 00:23:38,880
Dowager Consort Lady Hu

474
00:23:39,519 --> 00:23:40,599
is wicked of heart,

475
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,720
and in vying for favor,

476
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,119
has stopped at nothing.

477
00:23:43,279 --> 00:23:44,039
She exploited her own son,

478
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,559
deceiving superiors and inferiors alike.

479
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,880
From this day forward,

480
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,000
her title is revoked,

481
00:23:48,319 --> 00:23:49,400
she is demoted to commoner,

482
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,440
and confined to the Cold Palace.

483
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:51,559
So decreed.

484
00:23:58,599 --> 00:23:59,400
Royal Brother,

485
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,599
if I remember correctly,

486
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:02,880
this Lady Hu

487
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,480
should be your birth mother, right?

488
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:06,759
Come on.

489
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,680
Why don't you tell everyone,

490
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:11,519
how exactly your mother used you?

491
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,000
Liu Heng, don't go too far.

492
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:15,799
This is something Prince Shi must face himself.

493
00:24:25,480 --> 00:24:27,160
My mother did not use me.

494
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:30,880
She loved me.

495
00:24:32,079 --> 00:24:33,759
That's why she was so strict with me.

496
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:34,759
Oh.

497
00:24:34,759 --> 00:24:36,079
Is that so?

498
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,359
Hey,

499
00:24:38,359 --> 00:24:40,079
let me show you something else then.

500
00:24:42,559 --> 00:24:43,720
Look, what is this?

501
00:24:45,279 --> 00:24:46,559
Let me read it to you.

502
00:24:49,119 --> 00:24:49,680
"At a quarter past the Hour of the Dragon,

503
00:24:50,079 --> 00:24:51,279
one must rise from bed.

504
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:53,160
Within a quarter-hour limit,

505
00:24:53,279 --> 00:24:54,319
wash up and change clothes."

506
00:24:58,880 --> 00:24:59,720
Royal Brother,

507
00:25:00,119 --> 00:25:01,400
don't tell me

508
00:25:02,559 --> 00:25:04,519
this was also set by your mother.

509
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,559
Tsk.

510
00:25:05,559 --> 00:25:06,279
Huh.

511
00:25:07,799 --> 00:25:10,720
Living by this little book since childhood,

512
00:25:10,799 --> 00:25:12,759
your life must be exhausting indeed.

513
00:25:12,759 --> 00:25:13,559
Heh heh heh.

514
00:25:15,799 --> 00:25:16,599
Sigh.

515
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:19,519
Royal Brother,

516
00:25:19,519 --> 00:25:21,200
since childhood,

517
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:23,519
you've been Imperial Father's favorite son.

518
00:25:24,359 --> 00:25:25,480
When you were little,

519
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:26,680
you were gifted and brilliant beyond compare.

520
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,279
But look at you now.

521
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:31,480
Look what you've become.

522
00:25:32,359 --> 00:25:33,359
Heh heh.

523
00:25:34,279 --> 00:25:35,519
Liu Heng, haven't you said enough?

524
00:25:40,559 --> 00:25:41,039
Hmph.

525
00:25:44,119 --> 00:25:45,079
Heh heh heh.

526
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:47,119
A genius.

527
00:25:47,559 --> 00:25:49,599
I'm no genius.

528
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:52,880
When I was little, my mother told me,

529
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,359
because she was a Virgo,

530
00:25:57,279 --> 00:25:58,960
I had to be a Virgo too.

531
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:03,279
We had to live perfectly.

532
00:26:07,319 --> 00:26:09,279
Then she gave me this manual.

533
00:26:11,759 --> 00:26:12,519
Every single day,

534
00:26:13,119 --> 00:26:17,119
I followed this manual strictly,

535
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,759
studying the Four Books and Five Classics,

536
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:19,920
studying arithmetic,

537
00:26:20,359 --> 00:26:22,000
studying the qin.

538
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:25,680
Mother said

539
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,279
if I didn't study,

540
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,279
Imperial Father wouldn't love me.

541
00:26:35,599 --> 00:26:36,880
Haha.

542
00:26:39,599 --> 00:26:40,519
Later,

543
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:45,880
for the performance at Imperial Father's birthday banquet,

544
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,359
Mother made me memorize

545
00:26:49,359 --> 00:26:50,200
Zu's ratio.

546
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:53,160
I memorized it for so long,

547
00:26:55,079 --> 00:26:57,519
finally up to 200 decimal places.

548
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,680
But...

549
00:27:06,759 --> 00:27:09,119
But that day I was so nervous.

550
00:27:10,599 --> 00:27:12,599
I was just too nervous.

551
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,319
When Imperial Father asked me,

552
00:27:17,359 --> 00:27:18,599
when Imperial Father asked me,

553
00:27:20,279 --> 00:27:21,599
I got it wrong.

554
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,119
I got it wrong.

555
00:27:27,599 --> 00:27:29,119
I was wrong.

556
00:27:29,119 --> 00:27:29,759
I was wrong.

557
00:27:30,759 --> 00:27:32,160
All wrong.

558
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:33,799
All wrong.

559
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,279
And then...

560
00:27:46,359 --> 00:27:47,519
And then...

561
00:27:51,559 --> 00:27:53,279
Then Imperial Father got angry.

562
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:54,359
By the Mandate of Heaven,

563
00:27:54,559 --> 00:27:55,720
the Emperor proclaims:

564
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,119
Noble Consort Lady Hu

565
00:27:57,119 --> 00:27:58,400
is wicked of heart,

566
00:27:58,599 --> 00:27:59,279
and in vying for favor,

567
00:27:59,319 --> 00:28:00,880
has stopped at nothing.

568
00:28:01,079 --> 00:28:01,839
She exploited her own son,

569
00:28:01,839 --> 00:28:03,319
deceiving superiors and inferiors alike.

570
00:28:03,519 --> 00:28:04,680
From this day forward,

571
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:06,119
her title is revoked,

572
00:28:06,279 --> 00:28:07,359
she is demoted to commoner,

573
00:28:07,359 --> 00:28:08,519
and confined to the Cold Palace.

574
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:09,480
So decreed.

575
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:11,880
I thank His Majesty.

576
00:28:12,279 --> 00:28:13,160
Noble Consort,

577
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,279
please receive the decree.

578
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,440
Mother...

579
00:28:17,599 --> 00:28:19,160
I'm sorry.

580
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,480
I'll memorize it properly.

581
00:28:20,599 --> 00:28:21,720
I'll go memorize it right now.

582
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,519
Look at you.

583
00:28:25,519 --> 00:28:27,559
You've cried your face all dirty.

584
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:30,720
Don't ever get yourself dirty again.

585
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,880
Go wash up now, alright?

586
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,519
Guards!

587
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:35,640
I'm sorry.

588
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,759
I was wrong.

589
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:38,319
I'll memorize it properly.

590
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:40,880
I'll go memorize it right now.

591
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:43,799
Mother!

592
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:45,960
Mother!

593
00:28:48,119 --> 00:28:48,920
Mother!

594
00:28:50,319 --> 00:28:51,319
I'll memorize it properly.

595
00:28:52,279 --> 00:28:53,279
My child...

596
00:28:55,279 --> 00:28:56,119
Mother...

597
00:28:57,119 --> 00:28:58,720
I'll memorize it properly.

598
00:29:00,079 --> 00:29:01,599
I'll go memorize it right now.

599
00:29:05,119 --> 00:29:07,000
I shouldn't be like this.

600
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:11,400
I shouldn't be like this.

601
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,200
Prince Shi.

602
00:29:18,519 --> 00:29:20,359
Let Prince Shi rest for a while.

603
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:21,480
But...

604
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,079
The match isn't over. Are you quitting?

605
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:26,640
Compete?

606
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:27,680
Of course I'll compete!

607
00:29:31,279 --> 00:29:32,119
Good.

608
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:54,039
Prince Shi.

609
00:29:54,559 --> 00:29:56,119
You're awake.

610
00:29:57,079 --> 00:29:59,240
This is the consolation prize we won.

611
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,440
It's for you.

612
00:30:04,279 --> 00:30:05,720
What happened to me?

613
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:06,440
Huh?

614
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:07,519
No need to panic, Prince Shi.

615
00:30:07,599 --> 00:30:09,000
You just fainted.

616
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:10,799
We ran a simple test on you

617
00:30:10,799 --> 00:30:11,880
to check your condition.

618
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:13,720
Name?

619
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:14,519
Liu Rui.

620
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:15,720
Date of birth?

621
00:30:16,720 --> 00:30:18,000
December 13th.

622
00:30:18,319 --> 00:30:19,519
December 13th?

623
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:23,759
Then you should be a Sagittarius.

624
00:30:25,079 --> 00:30:26,279
I'm a Virgo.

625
00:30:26,359 --> 00:30:26,880
No, no.

626
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,799
I've studied Western astrology.

627
00:30:28,799 --> 00:30:30,880
December 13th is definitely a Sagittarius.

628
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:33,079
No, no, no. My mother is a Virgo.

629
00:30:33,599 --> 00:30:35,279
So I should be a Virgo too.

630
00:30:38,119 --> 00:30:38,880
Hmm.

631
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:41,640
Zodiac signs

632
00:30:42,119 --> 00:30:44,759
are based on date of birth.

633
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:50,880
Aren't zodiac signs hereditary?

634
00:30:51,759 --> 00:30:52,400
Prince Shi.

635
00:30:52,839 --> 00:30:54,559
Are you sure you're cured?

636
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:56,359
Yes, I am.

637
00:30:57,119 --> 00:30:58,279
I just realized

638
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:01,559
that as a Sagittarius, I crave freedom.

639
00:31:02,319 --> 00:31:04,599
Stop making excuses for going back on your word.

640
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:07,720
I...

641
00:31:09,279 --> 00:31:10,079
Uh...

642
00:31:10,519 --> 00:31:12,000
I hope the Princess will forgive me.

643
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:14,319
From now on, I

644
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:18,000
must follow the path of freedom.

645
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:20,680
I don't forgive you.

646
00:31:21,319 --> 00:31:22,960
If you want to leave, then go!

647
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:25,720
Thank you, Princess.

648
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:27,559
Ah.

649
00:31:27,559 --> 00:31:28,519
I suddenly remember

650
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:30,680
that day, running in the sunset.

651
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:31,720
Hahaha!

652
00:31:32,039 --> 00:31:34,359
Those were the steps of freedom.

653
00:31:34,359 --> 00:31:35,240
Hahaha!

654
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:40,720
Ugh.

655
00:31:42,319 --> 00:31:43,160
This Prince Shi...

656
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:47,559
One illness cured, another pops up!

657
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:49,759
He's driving me crazy!

658
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,680
Oh, come on now.

659
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:54,720
I think him letting go of everything to chase freedom

660
00:31:54,759 --> 00:31:56,119
is a kind of release too.

661
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,519
You have a point.

662
00:32:04,119 --> 00:32:05,279
Here, this is for you.

663
00:32:06,599 --> 00:32:07,400
Hmm?

664
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:10,000
Where'd you buy this slingshot?

665
00:32:10,599 --> 00:32:12,920
Looks like the gift your father gave you as a child, right?

666
00:32:14,759 --> 00:32:15,960
Yeah, pretty similar.

667
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:22,920
How'd you know my father gave me a slingshot?

668
00:32:23,279 --> 00:32:24,960
Oh, don't ask so many questions.

669
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:28,079
Ten City is on the border of Liang.

670
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:30,160
Just one mountain away from your Yan kingdom.

671
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,920
You haven't been home in so long.

672
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,319
Take a good look.

673
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,200
Qi Zhi.

674
00:32:51,079 --> 00:32:51,880
Thank you.

675
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:57,799
You're facing the wrong way.

676
00:32:57,799 --> 00:32:58,599
Oh!

677
00:33:04,279 --> 00:33:05,079
Here.
